  "remarks": "Paramilitary wing of the Revolutionary Committees Movement, a key component of the Qadhafi regime’s internal security system. Commanded by Hasan el-Kabir Al-Kadafi, cousin of Muammar Qadhafi.; Listing: Designated under the Autonomous Sanctions Regulations 2011 on 2 March 2012. Formerly listed on the RBA Consolidated List as 2011LBY0051. Instrument of first designation and declaration: Autonomous Sanctions (Designated Persons and Entities and Declared Persons – Libya) List 2012 [F2012L00481]\nRelisting on 12 January 2024.",
